&lt;p&gt;Talon.One is the most powerful incentives engine that unifies loyalty, promotions and gamification into one holistic platform.&amp;nbsp;Backed by enterprise-grade security and scalability, Talon.One empowers companies to build personalized, profitable promotions and loyalty programs using any data.&lt;/p&gt;
