&lt;li&gt;Write DWH pipelines and improve our overall DWH code to apply best practices and bring more efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a data team composed of various profiles, be at the center of all infrastructure decisions and work closely with other stakeholders from the R&amp;amp;D department, especially the DevOps team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
