&lt;p&gt;As our engineering organization scales, we are introducing a new Technical Governance and Enablement layer that sits right between Product Engineering, Architecture, and Platform/Infra. We are looking for a Technical Program Manager to become the operational engine, stakeholder shield, and planning partner for this critical new function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Production Engineering defines how production is run across R&amp;amp;D - from incidents and releases to operational workflows, reliability initiatives, and the systems that help engineers operate safely at scale. We treat this domain as an internal product.&lt;/p&gt;
